OL,5, Liz Truss has defended earnings at     
OL,6, energy companies amid soaring price    
OL,7, rises, saying profits should not be    
OL,8, considered "dirty and evil".           
OL,10,FThe Tory leadership hopeful said       
OL,11,Fwindfall taxes on profits - urged by   
OL,12,Fsome to fund help for households - were
OL,13,Fabout "bashing business".              
OL,15,FShe said cutting taxes was the best way
OL,16,Fto help with living costs over winter. 
OL,18,FBut rival Rishi Sunak said millions    
OL,19,Fwould be left at risk of destitution   
OL,20,Fwithout more energy payments.          
